print(self.name, '资金加100')
name_id = self.name[self.name.index('@'):]

基础领域术语库/quota_dscp.text:
# 找到所有的满意度quota，计算dscp的平均值
all_satisfaction = instance_base.instances.findAll(lambda elm: elm.name.startswith('满意度'))
all_values = all_satisfaction.map(lambda elm: elm.quota_dscp)

from functools import reduce
reduced = reduce(lambda x, y: x + y, all_values)
return reduced / len(all_values)

# 发货人资金--
# 快递公司资金++
print('发货人付款')

# 获得订单价格
order_id = token.data['order_id']
order = model.instance_base.findByName(order_id)

# 获得当前资金实例
sender_role = '物流概念/发货人'
sender = role[sender_role]
sender_name_id = sender.name[sender.name.index('@'):]
money_name = '资金' + sender_name_id
sender_money = sender.own_resource.find(lambda elm: elm.name == money_name)

# 更新资金
sender_money.amount = sender_money.amount - order.price

# 更新快递公司利润
logistics_profit = model.instance_base.findByName('快递公司利润')
logistics_profit.quota_dscp = logistics_profit.quota_dscp + order.price

# 重新计算发货人满意度
print('收件人确认收货')

# 获取送货时间
start_step = token.data['start_step']
delivery_step = model.step_count - start_step

# 获得订单价格
order_id = token.data['order_id']
order = model.instance_base.findByName(order_id)  # order.price

# 获得满意度实例
sender_role = '物流概念/发货人'
sender = role[sender_role]
sender_id = sender.name[sender.name.index('@'):]

satisfaction_name = '满意度' + sender_id
satisfaction = sender.all_quotas.find(lambda elm: elm.name == satisfaction_name)

alpha = 0.5
beta = 0.5

o_val = satisfaction.quota_dscp
n_val = o_val + alpha * (delivery_step - 5) + beta * (order.price - 20)

satisfaction.quota_dscp = n_val

# duration服从正态分布
print('快递公司运输')

# 生成一个订单信息（instance），订单信息中价格服从分布，订单信息的id存token。data里面
# model。instance——base。findByName
# instance。createInitInstance（）=》init——insatnce
print('发货人下单')

# 创建订单instance
order = model.instance_base.createInstance()

import random
import time

order_id = '订单' + str(time.time())

# 订单价格正态分布且为正整数
while True:
    order_price = round(random.normalvariate(20, 3))
    if order_price > 0:
        break

data = {
    'config': {},
    'name': order_id,
    'price': order_price,
    'data_properties': {},
    'type': []
}
order.loadJson(data)

# 订单id存token.data
token.data['order_id'] = order_id
token.data['start_step'] = model.step_count

# 增加快递单数
delivery_num = model.instance_base.findByName('快递单数')
delivery_num.quota_dscp = delivery_num.quota_dscp + 1

# 货物所有权从发货人=》快递公司
# model，role：参与者，执行参与者，token，process，
print('快递公司收货')

sender_role = '物流概念/发货人'
courier_role = '物流概念/快递公司'
sender = role[sender_role]
courier = role[courier_role]
sender_name_id = sender.name[sender.name.index('@'):]

# 找到二者持有的货物实例
sender_goods_name = '发货人货物' + sender_name_id
courier_goods_name = '快递公司货物'

sender_goods = sender.own_resource.find(lambda elm: elm.name == sender_goods_name)
sender_goods.amount = sender_goods.amount - 1

courier_goods = courier.own_resource.find(lambda elm: elm.name == courier_goods_name)
courier_goods.amount = courier_goods.amount + 1
